Josie Sedgwick https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Josie_Sedgwick 0 Josie Sedgwick (13 March 1898 – 30 April 1973) was an American film actress. She appeared in more than fifty films from 1914 to 1932. Sister of actor/director Edward Sedgwick. Josie_Sedgwick ( 13_March_1898 – 30_April_1973 ) was an_American_film_actress . She appeared in more_than_fifty_films from 1914 to 1932 .
